      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it an excellent choice for someone seeking a dependable and attractive car. The exterior paint still holds a great luster, though there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scratch on the rear bumper consistent with normal use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with the leather seats showing only light creasing on the driver's side bolster. All electronic features, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully functional. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with a complete service history available for review, ensuring peace of mind for the next owner.",
